org.cpsolver.ifs.solution

Class Solution<V extends Variable<V,T>,T extends Value<V,T>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cpsolver.ifs.solution.Solution<V,T>
  • Type Parameters:
    V - Variable
    T - Value

    public class Solution<V extends Variable<V,T>,T extends Value<V,T>>
extends Object
    Generic solution.

    It consist from the model and information about current iteration and solution time.
    Version:
